<h1><span id="King.27s_Gambit_Accepted.2C_4.Bc4"></span><span id="King's_Gambit_Accepted,_4.Bc4">King's Gambit Accepted, 4.Bc4</span></h1>
<p>With 4.Bc4, White ignores Black's pawn advance in favor of development. Black can now either continue his development with 4...Bg7 or attempt to unseat White's knight with 4...g4.
</p>
<p>1.e4 e5 2.f4 exf4 3.Nf3 g5 4.Bc4
